room_title: Escape room "Vacancy" by The Room VB in Virginia Beach
review: Best escape room I've done to date (Vacancy). Rooms are beautiful and well thought out, and the staff is great. Will definitely be back!

room_title: Escape room "Vacancy" by The Room VB in Virginia Beach
review: We had a great time! We were told Vacancy was the hardest room and they normally don't allow two people to book this room. But we were only two clues away from escaping! Loved the challenges and the room in and of itself! If me and my friend come back to Virginia Beach we definitely will be trying another one of their rooms!
